folder: Gun Hill Road (East) & Barnes Avenue, Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: Gun Hill Road (East) - Barnes Avenue
text:
(1)
E. Gunhill Road, south side, east from Barnes to Bronxwood Avenues, showing Evander Childs High School. The view is eastward across Italian gardens from Tilden Street.
May 11, 1938.

P. L. Sperr

(2)
The same, from a slightly different angle.
May 11, 1938.

P. L. Sperr
